text: Yavor Hristov is an archer from Bulgaria. Hristov competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Yavor Vasilev HRISTOV He was born on 25 March 1976.Yavor Hristov == References == Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian archers Category:Olympians for Bulgaria
